{"tid":2201010,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"陳志全加入熱血公民好人經濟圈！！！","createTime":"2020-09-13T12:27:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T08:23:56.000Z","uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c2aafd399303b009c50b94a27c876ab5627430b5","tid":2201010,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:27:11.000Z","msg":"人大早前決定全體立法會議員延任不少於一年，人民力量陳志全（慢必）自言「八九成都會離開」，未來一年都有唔少大計，包括已經開定Patreon帳戶供訂閱。慢必同Emily講，呢段時間希望經營番社交網絡，除咗主打強項嘅時事、議會評論之外，都希望拉闊啲，講吓電影軟銷公民教育，甚至講吓中國歷史朝代、<span class=\"gold\">考慮做《紅樓夢》章節導賞。</span>另外佢仲想寫書，除咗講議會抗爭，都想整理吓香港同志運動歷史、司法覆核案件等。<br />\n<br />\n慢必話Patreon剛剛開設，10月正式有內容，暫時唔算好多人訂閱；大計多多，但慢必話一年其實唔係好多時間，做到一兩樣已經好好。<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200903/s00002/1599070172481/%E3%80%90emily%E3%80%91%E4%B9%9D%E6%88%90%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83-%E6%85%A2%E5%BF%85%E9%96%8Bpatreon%E8%AC%9B%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E5%8F%8A%E7%B4%85%E6%A8%93%E5%A4%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200903%2Fs00002%2F1599070172481%2F%25E3%2580%2590emily%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25B9%259D%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%259B%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%2585%25A2%25E5%25BF%2585%25E9%2596%258Bpatreon%25E8%25AC%259B%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E5%258F%258A%25E7%25B4%2585%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25A4%25A2&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8HpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=73f21e2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200903%2Fs00002%2F1599070172481%2F%25E3%2580%2590emily%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25B9%259D%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%259B%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%2585%25A2%25E5%25BF%2585%25E9%2596%258Bpatreon%25E8%25AC%259B%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E5%258F%258A%25E7%25B4%2585%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25A4%25A2&h=b0ca3643\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200903/s00002/1